com.metrics.common.sets

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.AbstractMap<K,V>
      • java.util.HashMap<K,V>
        • java.util.LinkedHashMap<String,Object>
          • com.metrics.common.sets.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Map<String,Object>

    public class Item
extends LinkedHashMap<String,Object>
    Represents an item, the basic element from which sets are composed. An item is a collection of key-value pairs containing a single descriptive unit that can be stored, searched, retrieved, altered, or exported.
    Author:
    search
